    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif\">At 20th level, you've mastered your craft and have perfected your energy source. Your power charges now degrade and lose power after 7 days. When using the power surge feature, there's no longer a chance of the power charge detonating. Instead, if you roll a 1, you fail to gain the additional 2d6 to your charge potency.</span></p><h4><span style=\"font-family:rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif\">Additionally, you have advantage on any ability check made using tools.</span></h4>",
